  "summary": "Updated procmail packages fix security vulnerability",
  "details": "A flaw was found in the loadbuf function in formisc.c. When the buffer\nis too small, the function tries to resize it, but only by Bsize (=128)\nbytes. This is not necessarily enough and could cause denial of service.\n",
